#!/usr/bin/osascript

# =============================================================================
# Invert Screen Colors
# http://apple.stackexchange.com/questions/127255/how-to-flash-screen-from-command-line
#
# In order to work, the Accessibility keyboard shortcut needs to be enabled:
# http://b.ustin.co/DSDF
#
# Version 0.1.0
# =============================================================================

tell application "System Events"
key code 28 using {command down, control down, option down}
end tell
